      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490502
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa721",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa722",
      "text": " > [@nicoanime_PR https://twitter.com/nicoanime_PR/status/1829402807398735967]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa723",
      "text": " > 【お知らせ】",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa724",
      "text": " > 本日から9/6(金)14:59まで「 #2024春アニメ 」テレビ見逃し作品の未配信話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa725",
      "text": " > 全39作品、総話数：133話を無料配信中！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa726",
      "text": " > 対象作品・話数は下記URLよりご確認ください。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa727",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa728",
      "text": " > 皆様のご視聴・コメントをお待ちしております。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa729",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72a",
      "text": " > ▼詳細",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72b",
      "text": " > https://blog.nicovideo.jp/niconews/227395.html ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72c",
      "text": " >  #ニコニコアニメ復活 ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72d",
      "text": "  マジ？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72e",
      "text": "  神対応すぎる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa72f",
      "text": "  権利まわりの問題もあるだろうから、[ニコニコ大障害]で配信できなかったものはそのままになるかと思ってた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa730",
      "text": "  確率を低く見積もってた対応だけに、めちゃくちゃ驚いてる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa731",
      "text": "\t\tすごい[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa732",
      "text": "\t\tオススメあれば知りたい[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa733",
      "text": "\t\t [2024春アニメ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa734",
      "text": "\t\t\t井戸端にガチなアニオタ居て欲しい(願望)[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa735",
      "text": "\t\t\tscrapboxに範囲を広げていいなら、[/sno2wman/sno2wman.icon][/ci7lus/ci7lus.icon]さんあたりが該当しそう[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa736",
      "text": "\t\t\tマンガを紹介しまくっていた[hatori.icon]さんを思い出す[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa737",
      "text": "\t\t\tああー[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa738",
      "text": "\t\t\tScrapbox民に詳しい人　がいたw[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa739",
      "text": "\t\t昨日の[ダンジョン飯]一挙放送（1～13話）は盛り上がってた[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa73a",
      "text": "\t\t\t残りは今日の夕方から",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa73b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://live.nicovideo.jp/watch/lv345596657 ダンジョン飯 14～24話一挙放送 - 2024/8/31(土) 18:00開始 - ニコニコ生放送]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a019c8000000000002fa73c",
      "text": "\t\t\tコメント付きで見られるアニメは良いものだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778490497,
      "updated": 1778490497
